nd u2u fostering collaboration with partner institutions for building capacity in the geosciences we are working to develop a faculty staff and student body that reflect the diversity of our national communities and international partners to learn more visit the oma web site stanford university school of earth sciences 397 panama mall ca 94305 2210 mitchell building 101 tel 650 723 2544 2012 stanford university related resources employment opportunities hartley conference center health and safety computing resources room resources how can we help maps & directions stanfordwho office of the registrar contact us connect to earth sciences facebook itunes u twitter youtube
